This is a pure CSS transliteration of names and agencies on the main vote page for PRODUCE X 101 located at http://produce-x-101.mnet.com/pc/vote

This is only for that specific page, and the ranking page as of version 1.0.0, and does not provide transliterations or translations for anything besides the traineesâ€™ names and agencies. To avoid confusion, I used the spellings on their profiles on this site.

This is built off of my previous theme for PRODUCE48 which can be found here:
https://userstyles.org/styles/159853/produce-48-vote-page-name-agency-transliteration

If you spot any errors, please contact me: @Sei#2975 on Discord, @XinChun93 on Twitter, /u/yaycupcake on Reddit.
